The first blog posts written in French about the earthquake in Haiti have come
from outside the country, announcing terrible news of the [Presidential Palace
](http://www.metropolehaiti.com/metropole/full_une_fr.php?id=16288),[ a
hospital ](http://projets-maryse.blogspot.com/2010/01/73.html) and other
buildings collapsing and also of the [threat of a
tsunami](http://blogmtl.com/2010/01/12/international-haiti-un-puissant-
seisme/). According to
[MetropoleHaiti](http://www.metropolehaiti.com/metropole/full_une_fr.php?id=16281),
The USA have already proposed humanitarian assistance.

